  <brief_title>Post Operative Quality of Life and Pain in Ankle Fractures: Cast Versus Functional Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Post Operative Evaluation of Quality of Life and Pain in Ankle Fractures: Cast Immobilisation Versus Functional Treatment</official_title>
